oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:title: Bob Wills Show -1946-04-23 - Part 1
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:description: Bob Wills Show sponsored by Fisher's Zoom cereal, originally broadcast 1946-04-23, part 1. Featuring Bob Wills, Tommy Duncan, Lester 'Junior' Barnard, Dean McKinney, Evelyn McKinney, Noel Boggs, Millard Kelso, and host Jack Webb.
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:creator: Bob Wills; Texas Playboys
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dcterms:tableOfContents: Opening statement (Jack Webb) [interrupted] -- Theme (San Antonio Rose) [interrupted] -- Opening statement (Bob Wills) [interrupted] -- Liberty [interrupted] -- Zoom commercial (Jack Webb) [interrupted] -- Ride On! (My Prairie Pinto) (Tommy Duncan) -- Jack Webb introduces the next song -- Take Me Back To Tulsa (Tommy Duncan) -- Zoom jingle -- Jack Webb talks about the Zoom contest -- Hawaiian War Chant -- Jack Webb and Bob Wills introduce the next song -- Little Betty Brown (Bob Wills fiddle) -- Jack Webb introduces the next song
